title: Glift 1.1
description:
New Version of Glift!

User Features:
- Ko Support
- Figures!
- SGF FF[1-3] support
- Mousewheel support
- Easier Tygem (Gib-files) support

Engineering Improvements:
- UI Rewrite
- Type Checking

title: Near Future
description: Issues that are planned on being addressed in the near future.

title: Unplanned Backlog
description: A backlog of issues that are not a high priority. Some might get worked on in the future; others might never get worked on, but it's useful to keep them around for if other people want to comment on the issue.

title: GPub
description: GPub is the next generation of Go publishing software.  Several changes are needed in Glift to support GPub.

title: Obsolete
description: Milestone bucket for issues that are no longer relevant for some reason or another.

title: Launch on Go Game Guru
description: Milestone for launching site-wide on Go Game Guru.  Targeted at July 27th.  This is naturally a sprint, so only the top-priority bugs are getting fixed.
